nio/lol/tsconfig.json` and missing `src/vite-env.d.ts`\n\n---\n\n### 3. What Looks Good\n\n- **`vite.config.ts`**: Clean, correct. Path alias `@` is properly set up. Sass `modern-compiler` API is the right choice for modern sass.\n- **`tsconfig.json`**: Strict mode is fully enabled with all the strict sub-flags. `noUncheckedIndexedAccess` is a strong choice. `bundler` module resolution is correct for Vite. Path alias matches vite config.\n- **`index.html`**: Minimal, correct.\n- **`src/main.tsx`**: Proper null check on root element, StrictMode enabled, clean.\n- **`src/App.tsx`**: Minimal placeholder, named export, no unnecessary boilerplate.\n- **`eslint.config.js`**: Flat config format, TypeScript + React hooks + React refresh all wired correctly. Underscore-prefixed unused args pattern is a good convention.\n- **File naming**: All files follow conventions.\n- **No comments in code**: Followed.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Item | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| Dependencies installed | PASS |\n| vite.config.ts | NEEDS CHANGE (missing test config) |\n| tsconfig.json | MINOR (missing vite-env.d.ts) |\n| index.html | PASS |\n| src/main.tsx | PASS |\n| src/App.tsx | PASS |\n| eslint.config.js | PASS |\n| package.json scripts | NEEDS CHANGE (lint --fix in check, no prettier config) |\n| `bun run dev` | PASS |\n| `bun run check` | PASS (but semantically incorrect due to --fix) |\n| `bun run build` | PASS |\n| `bun run test` | PASS (vacuously, no tests exist and infra is misconfigured) |\n\n**Two blocking issues** (vitest environment, prettier config gap) and **two minor issues** (lint --fix in check, missing vite-env.d.ts) must be addressed before this can be approved."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":265,"cache_read_input_tokens":16934,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":265},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"re